<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>No Cap: Love, Dating & The Real Antidote 🕊️🔥</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700;800;900&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --neon-pink: #ff2d78;
    --neon-blue: #00d4ff;
    --gold: #ffd60a;
    --purple: #9b5de5;
    --mint: #06ffa5;
    --dark: #08080f;
    --dark2: #111120;
    --glass: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    --glass-border: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--dark);
    font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    overflow: hidden;
    height: 100vh;
    width: 100vw;
    user-select: none;
  }

  /* ===== LOGO STYLES ===== */
  .logo-container {
    position: fixed;
    top: 16px;
    right: 30px;
    z-index: 1000;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  .logo-container:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }
  .logo-container img { height: 40px; width: auto; }

  /* ===== BACKGROUND PARTICLES ===== */
  #bg-canvas {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* ===== SLIDE WRAPPER ===== */
  .slides-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100vh;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .slide {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 40px;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.15s;
  }

  .slide.active {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: all;
  }

  @keyframes slideUp {
    from { transform: translateY(60px); opacity: 0; }
    to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes popIn {
    0% { transform: scale(0.7) rotate(-5deg); opacity: 0; }
    70% { transform: scale(1.05) rotate(1deg); }
    100% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg); opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes slideLeft {
    from { transform: translateX(-80px); opacity: 0; }
    to { transform: translateX(0); opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes slideRight {
    from { transform: translateX(80px); opacity: 0; }
    to { transform: translateX(0); opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes glow {
    0%,100% { text-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--neon-pink), 0 0 40px var(--neon-pink); }
    50% { text-shadow: 0 0 40px var(--neon-pink), 0 0 80px var(--neon-pink), 0 0 120px var(--neon-pink); }
  }
  @keyframes float {
    0%,100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-12px); }
  }
  @keyframes bounce {
    0%,100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-8px); }
  }
  @keyframes shimmer {
    0% { background-position: -200% center; }
    100% { background-position: 200% center; }
  }
  @keyframes pulse-glow {
    0%,100% { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,45,120,0.3), 0 0 40px rgba(155,93,229,0.2); }
    50% { box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255,45,120,0.6), 0 0 80px rgba(155,93,229,0.4); }
  }
  @keyframes wave-anim {
    0%,100% { height: 6px; }
    50% { height: 30px; }
  }

  /* ===== TYPOGRAPHY ===== */
  .title-mega {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(60px, 12vw, 130px);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .title-big {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 7vw, 90px);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .title-med {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4.5vw, 56px);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .body-text {
    font-size: clamp(14px, 2vw, 20px);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .caption {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: clamp(10px, 1.3vw, 14px);
    opacity: 0.6;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ===== COLORS ===== */
  .pink { color: var(--neon-pink); }
  .blue { color: var(--neon-blue); }
  .gold { color: var(--gold); }
  .purple { color: var(--purple); }
  .mint { color: var(--mint); }
  .white { color: #fff; }

  .grad-pink-blue {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--neon-pink), var(--neon-blue));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  .grad-gold-mint {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), var(--mint));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  .grad-shimmer {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--neon-pink), var(--gold), var(--neon-blue), var(--neon-pink));
    background-size: 400% auto;
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    animation: shimmer 3s linear infinite;
  }

  /* ===== GLASS CARDS ===== */
  .glass-card {
    background: var(--glass);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 24px 30px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  }
  .neon-card-pink {
    background: rgba(255, 45, 120, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 45, 120, 0.3);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 24px 30px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255,45,120,0.1);
  }
  .neon-card-blue {
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 24px 30px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,212,255,0.1);
  }
  .neon-card-gold {
    background: rgba(255, 214, 10, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 214, 10, 0.3);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 24px 30px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255,214,10,0.1);
  }

  /* ===== TAGS / BADGES ===== */
  .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .tag-pink { background: rgba(255,45,120,0.2); border: 1px solid var(--neon-pink); color: var(--neon-pink); }
  .tag-blue { background: rgba(0,212,255,0.2); border: 1px solid var(--neon-blue); color: var(--neon-blue); }
  .tag-gold { background: rgba(255,214,10,0.2); border: 1px solid var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }
  .tag-mint { background: rgba(6,255,165,0.2); border: 1px solid var(--mint); color: var(--mint); }
  .tag-purple { background: rgba(155,93,229,0.2); border: 1px solid var(--purple); color: var(--purple); }

  /* ===== DECORATIVE ELEMENTS ===== */
  .deco-circle {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .emoji-float {
    position: absolute;
    font-size: 2rem;
    animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  /* ===== NAVIGATION ===== */
  .nav-bar {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 30px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 50px;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  }
  .nav-btn {
    background: none;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    color: white;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-btn:hover {
    background: var(--neon-pink);
    border-color: var(--neon-pink);
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }
  .slide-counter {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    min-width: 60px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .dot-nav { display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center; }
  .dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .dot.active {
    background: var(--neon-pink);
    width: 20px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--neon-pink);
  }

  /* ===== PROGRESS BAR ===== */
  .progress-bar {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--neon-pink), var(--neon-blue));
    transition: width 0.4s ease;
    z-index: 100;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--neon-pink);
  }

  /* ===== SLIDE-SPECIFIC LAYOUTS ===== */
  #slide-0 {
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 50%, rgba(255,45,120,0.2) 0%, transparent 60%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 30%, rgba(0,212,255,0.15) 0%, transparent 60%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 80%, rgba(155,93,229,0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
  }

  .grid-2 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 900px;
  }
  .grid-3 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 900px;
  }
  .flex-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 860px;
  }

  .anim-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateX(-30px);
  }
  .slide.active .anim-item:nth-child(1) { animation: slideLeft 0.5s 0.3s forwards; }
  .slide.active .anim-item:nth-child(2) { animation: slideLeft 0.5s 0.5s forwards; }
  .slide.active .anim-item:nth-child(3) { animation: slideLeft 0.5s 0.7s forwards; }
  .slide.active .anim-item:nth-child(4) { animation: slideLeft 0.5s 0.9s forwards; }
  .slide.active .anim-item:nth-child(5) { animation: slideLeft 0.5s 1.1s forwards; }

  .bullet-icon {
    min-width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .slide.active .anim-up { animation: slideUp 0.6s 0.1s both; }
  .slide.active .anim-up-2 { animation: slideUp 0.6s 0.3s both; }
  .slide.active .anim-up-3 { animation: slideUp 0.6s 0.5s both; }
  .slide.active .anim-up-4 { animation: slideUp 0.6s 0.7s both; }
  .slide.active .anim-up-5 { animation: slideUp 0.6s 0.9s both; }
  .slide.active .anim-up-6 { animation: slideUp 0.6s 1.1s both; }
  .slide.active .anim-pop { animation: popIn 0.6s 0.2s both; }
  .slide.active .anim-fade { animation: fadeIn 0.8s 0.4s both; }
  .slide.active .anim-right { animation: slideRight 0.6s 0.3s both; }

  .slide-header {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .slide-header .caption {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: block;
  }

  .triangle-viz {
    position: relative;
    width: 280px;
    height: 280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .tri-node {
    position: absolute;
    width: 70px;
    height: 70px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 900;
    border: 2px solid;
  }
  .tri-top { top: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: rgba(255,214,10,0.15); border-color: var(--gold); animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .tri-left { bottom: 0; left: 0; background: rgba(255,45,120,0.15); border-color: var(--neon-pink); animation: float 3s 1s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .tri-right { bottom: 0; right: 0; background: rgba(0,212,255,0.15); border-color: var(--neon-blue); animation: float 3s 2s ease-in-out infinite; }

  .verse-box {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--neon-pink);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: rgba(255,45,120,0.05);
    border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* Song card */
  .song-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,45,120,0.1), rgba(155,93,229,0.1));
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 30px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 760px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    animation: pulse-glow 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .song-wave {
    display: flex;
    gap: 4px;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-end;
    height: 30px;
    margin: 12px 0;
  }
  .wave-bar {
    width: 4px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    background: var(--neon-pink);
    animation: wave-anim 1s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .wave-bar:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0s; background: var(--neon-pink); }
  .wave-bar:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; background: var(--purple); }
  .wave-bar:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.2s; background: var(--neon-blue); }
  .wave-bar:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.3s; background: var(--mint); }
  .wave-bar:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.4s; background: var(--gold); }
  .wave-bar:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.3s; background: var(--neon-blue); }
  .wave-bar:nth-child(7) { animation-delay: 0.2s; background: var(--purple); }
  .wave-bar:nth-child(8) { animation-delay: 0.1s; background: var(--neon-pink); }
  .wave-bar:nth-child(9) { animation-delay: 0s; background: var(--gold); }

  .stat-big {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 72px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .step-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  #slide-11 {
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(155,93,229,0.25) 0%, rgba(255,45,120,0.1) 40%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .touch-hint {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 90px;
    right: 30px;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    animation: bounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  /* Lyric line styles */
  .lyric-section-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    margin-top: 14px;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }
  .lyric-line {
    font-size: clamp(12px, 1.6vw, 16px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
  }
  .lyric-line.highlight {
    color: var(--neon-pink);
    font-size: clamp(13px, 1.8vw, 18px);
    font-weight: 900;
  }
  .lyric-line.chorus {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 800;
  }
  .lyric-line.bridge {
    color: var(--neon-blue);
    font-weight: 800;
  }
  .lyric-scroll {
    overflow-y: auto;
    max-height: calc(100vh - 180px);
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 760px;
    padding: 0 10px 10px;
    scrollbar-width: thin;
    scrollbar-color: rgba(255,45,120,0.3) transparent;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- LOGO CONTAINER -->
<div class="logo-container">
  <img src="https://i.imgur.com/3lLW585.png" alt="Logo">
</div>

<!-- PROGRESS BAR -->
<div class="progress-bar" id="progress"></div>

<!-- PARTICLES -->
<canvas id="bg-canvas"></canvas>

<!-- ==================== SLIDES ==================== -->
<div class="slides-container" id="slides">

  <!-- SLIDE 0: COVER -->
  <div class="slide active" id="slide-0">
    <div class="deco-circle" style="width:400px;height:400px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(255,45,120,0.15),transparent);top:-100px;right:-100px;"></div>
    <div class="deco-circle" style="width:300px;height:300px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(0,212,255,0.12),transparent);bottom:-50px;left:-80px;"></div>
    <div class="emoji-float" style="top:15%;left:8%;animation-delay:0s;">🔥</div>
    <div class="emoji-float" style="top:20%;right:10%;animation-delay:0.5s;">🕊️</div>
    <div class="emoji-float" style="bottom:25%;left:5%;animation-delay:1s;">💕</div>
    <div class="emoji-float" style="bottom:20%;right:8%;animation-delay:1.5s;">✨</div>
    <div class="anim-up" style="margin-bottom:12px;">
      <span class="tag tag-pink">Youth Special Series</span>
    </div>
    <div class="anim-up-2">
      <div class="title-mega grad-shimmer" style="margin-bottom:8px;">NO CAP</div>
    </div>
    <div class="anim-up-3">
      <div class="title-med white" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:20px;opacity:0.9;">
        Love, Dating & The <span class="pink">Real</span> Antidote
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="anim-up-4" style="text-align:center;max-width:560px;margin-bottom:30px;">
      <p class="body-text" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">
        POV: Kamu lagi nyari cinta, tapi malah nemu red flags atau rasa kosong yang nggak abis-abis. Yuk, kita spill the tea pakai kacamata Tuhan dan sains. 🤍
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="anim-up-5" style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;">
      <span class="tag tag-blue">🧠 Science</span>
      <span class="tag tag-mint">📖 Alkitab</span>
      <span class="tag tag-gold">💡 Real Talk</span>
      <span class="tag tag-purple">🎵 Musik</span>
    </div>
    <div class="anim-fade" style="position:absolute;bottom:100px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);text-align:center;">
      <p class="caption" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);">11 slides • tap or press arrow keys</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SLIDE 1 -->
  <div class="slide" id="slide-1">
    <div style="width:100%;max-width:860px;">
      <div class="slide-header anim-up">
        <span class="caption pink">Slide 01</span>
        <div class="title-big white">Kenapa Harus <span class="grad-pink-blue">Bahas Ini?</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-col" style="margin-top:20px;">
        <div class="anim-item">
          <div class="bullet-icon" style="background:rgba(255,45,120,0.15);border:1px solid var(--neon-pink);">📱</div>
          <div class="glass-card" style="flex:1;">
            <p class="body-text white">Kita tiap hari di-<span class="pink">FYP</span> sama konten romance yang bikin baper. Ada yang manifest jodoh, kena ghosting, sampe healing dari broken home.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="anim-item">
          <div class="bullet-icon" style="background:rgba(0,212,255,0.15);border:1px solid var(--neon-blue);">🌍</div>
          <div class="neon-card-blue" style="flex:1;">
            <p class="body-text white">Dunia bilang: <span class="blue">"Cari pacar biar bahagia."</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="anim-item">
          <div class="bullet-icon" style="background:rgba(255,214,10,0.15);border:1px solid var(--gold);">📖</div>
          <div class="neon-card-gold" style="flex:1;">
            <p class="body-text white">Tapi <span class="gold">Alkitab</span> punya Blueprint yang jauh lebih keren dari itu. Kita belajar dari <strong>The OG Couple: Adam & Hawa!</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="anim-up-5" style="margin-top:20px;">
        <div class="verse-box">
          <p class="body-text" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);">"Hanya dekat Allah saja aku tenang." — <span class="pink">Mazmur 62:2</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SLIDE 2 -->
  <div class="slide" id="slide-2">
    <div style="width:100%;max-width:900px;">
      <div class="slide-header anim-up">
        <span class="caption blue">Slide 02</span>
        <div class="title-big white">Habitat & <span class="grad-pink-blue">Sumber Life</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:18px;gap:14px;">
